text: @GovInslee If slowing the spread of COVID-19 is as important and necessary as some of you claim, waiting TWO WEEKS to implement such critically important rules isn’t smart or science - it’s just stupid and political. If it’s so critical than reduce things now. That’s how emergencies work.
